{"tid":2112280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】  我地唔應該再舉「美國」旗…","createTime":"2020-07-17T07:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T22:52:46.000Z","uid":154486,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7855b54f6229475bcabee049c3eb8cac1cf3946d","tid":2112280,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"係Twitter見到所羅門Retweet手足，有少少感觸<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1283868922144370688?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1283868922144370688%3Fs%3D19&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=05040cea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1283868922144370688%3Fs%3D19&h=7f6c55d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1283868922144370688?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">手足話，呢支旗唔係代表一個外國國家<br />\n呢支旗係香港係代表「希望同自由」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我提議，各位手足以後提到呢支旗果陣<br />\n可以唔稱呼呢支做「美國國旗」<br />\n因為呢支旗唔係一支普通既國旗咁簡單<br />\n，因為佢可以唔一定代表美國<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\">我地應該叫番呢支旗既本名：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">「星條旗」或者「花旗」<br />\nStar-Spangled Banner</span></strong><br />\nStar {士-Ben-高-ed}  Banner </span></p>"},{"pid":"12872972149504698de2672d483d6fddcb1ad072","tid":2112280,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"做左標題黨sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022b24787e10f70fe81d91184ed26b6a81479568","tid":2112280,"uid":88743,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"琴日pompeo都係咁講<br />\n話香港人呢一年成日揮香港旗<br />\n係因為世界上搵唔到一支更能代表人權民主與自由既旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail